txt.en: You found a note signed with an 'S' upon the body of a brigand while trying to recover the goods stolen from Oserley.
'This is dire news if Saruman seeks to undermine our people. You should take this note to Thane Ordlac...he will wish to know what has transpired. He is young, but he is wise.'
Bring the brigands' note to Thane Ordlac
Thane Ordlac is in the Mead Hall of Oserley.\n\nDudsig asked you to bring the note you found to Thane Ordlac.
'Dudsig sent you with this note? Let us take a look at it.\n\n'It appears, my friend, that we have a traitor among us. This note implies that one of my retainers may be in league with Saruman.'
